  &lt;p&gt;Today, there are nearly &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/limra--nearly-5-million-more-us-households-have-life-insurance-coverage-300335782.html"&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;5 million&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; more households in the U.S. with a life insurance policy, compared to 2010&amp;mdash;and for good reason. What&amp;rsquo;s unique about life insurance is that unlike many other types of insurnce such as home and auto, the number one reason to buy life insurance is &lt;strong&gt;love&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

